    "Hekate_Atmosphere": {
        "changelog": [
            "======================================",
            "   What's Changed ? (Hekate & Nyx)    ",
            "--------------------------------------\n",
            "◆ Version: 6.2.1&1.6.3 > 6.2.2&1.6.4\n",
            "- HOS 19.0.0 support.               \n",
            "- L4T: Update ARC to v6               ",
            "  Added latency decoupling via        ",
            "  ram_oc_opt.                       \n",
            "- Fixed an issue on Oled skus where   ",
            "  they couldn't automatically reboot  ",
            "  to OFW if stock failed.           \n",
            "- Easter Egg got updated to v2.5.3    ",
            "  Reduced power draw even more while  ",
            "  idle every frame.                 \n",
            "- Flash Android button will now have  ", 
            "  the version that was selected in    ",
            "  partition scheme.                 \n",
            "- GPT partition in MBR summary is now ",
            "  purple in order to not be confused  ",
            "  with Android partitions.          \n",
            "- Battery info can now show up to 6 PD",
            "  profiles.                         \n",
            "======================================",
            "    What's Changed ? (Atmosphère)     ",
            "--------------------------------------\n",
            "◆ Version: 1.7.1 > 1.8.0           \n",
            "- Basic support was added for 19.0.0.\n",
            "  The console should boot and atmo    ",
            "  should be fully functional.       \n",
            "  However, not all modules have been  ",
            "  fully updated to reflect the latest ",
            "  changes.                          \n",
            "  There shouldn't be anything user    ",
            "  visible resulting from this, but it ",
            "  will be addressed in a future atmo  ",
            "  update.                           \n",
            "  There is still one action item from ",
            "  18.0.0 to be addressed, as well.  \n",
            "- exosphère was updated to reflect the",
            "  latest official secure monitor      ",
            "  behavior.                         \n",
            "- mesosphère was updated to reflect   ",
            "  the latest official kernel behavior.\n",
            "- loader was updated to reflect the   ",
            "  latest official behavior.         \n",
            "- pm was updated to reflect the latest",
            "  official behavior.                \n",
            "- ro was updated to reflect the latest",
            "  official behavior.                \n",
            "- creport's file acces patterns were  ",
            "  optimized, greatly improving        ",
            "  performance when generating a crash ",
            "  report.                           \n",
            "- Atmosphère now uses relr relocations",
            "  where possible.                   \n",
            "  This reduces the filesize of a      ",
            "  number of atmosphère's modules.   \n",
            "- A number of minor issues were fixed ",
            "  and improvements were made,         ",
            "  including.                        \n",
            "  Support was fixed for running Atmo  ",
            "  on newer units with specific Hynix, ",
            "  Micron DRAM chips.                \n",
            "- General system stability improvement",
            "  to enhance the user's experience. \n",
            "======================================"
        ],
